{"tid":261423,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"關於屋企裝修加Lan插頭問題","createTime":"2017-05-28T12:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T15:07:50.000Z","uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8aed9b275e3b7c2172ca905df38a9a31a576b8","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"請問如果屋企要整2個Lan位(一主一副)，即一個入屋插Router再分出嚟去電腦，另一個去電視果度用來插(家用遊戲機/智能電視)，咁樣係唔係淨係需要2個Lan插位？<br />\n屋企第一次大裝修，唔知Lan位點樣搞，聽d朋友話除咗本身個Router(TPlink)之外要再加一個Switch先至得，唔知牆身要做幾多個Lan位，係唔係2個就可以？"},{"pid":"68985c00517c59ba1f079675310e36225778ee27","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"本身用HKBN BB100"},{"pid":"6c8dec0afaf80aa07c4961bd3efd81d2752a620c","tid":261423,"uid":13537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"有冇平面圖<br />\n你HKBN入屋位係唔係電視位到<br />\n你router又會放邊<br />\n電腦又放邊<br />\n<br />\n我先當Router放電視位<br />\n<br />\n如果HKBN入屋位係電視位<br />\n咁就好簡易<br />\nRouter放電視位<br />\n做一集暗喉拉LAN線做插位  電視位到電腦位<br />\nHKBN插router WAN 一般都4個LAN,唔洗買switch都夠用<br />\nLAN1 去插位比電腦用<br />\nLAN2 比遊戲機<br />\n<br />\n如果HKBN入屋位係唔係電視位<br />\n做一集暗喉 HKBN入屋位到電視位<br />\n叫HKBN師傅拉線直接到電視位<br />\n再做一集暗喉拉LAN線做插位  電視位到電腦位<br />\n之後同上面一樣"},{"pid":"067e96c7ebedb805e2fca85bbf70e8c20dba38a8","tid":261423,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"too long didn't read<br />\n同裝修師傳講邊度要上網 邊度做個位比你<br />\n之後再搵上網公司穿線"},{"pid":"cca91fd7c76d159ac38cfd8522b8ff5bf367840f","tid":261423,"uid":11082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"Lan線位最好用獨立喉<br />\n第時成條線拉過都冇咁煩<br />\n光纖最好少彎位"},{"pid":"cf9109e1ca09e7e7b70fc2c1d1d2b907d54c995a","tid":261423,"uid":76198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>too long didn't read<br />\n同裝修師傳講邊度要上網 邊度做個位比你<br />\n之後再搵上網公司穿線</blockquote><br />\n搵上網公司隨時拉d四芯俾你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且都唔一定幫你拉<br />\n自己買一箱100M嘅 cat6俾師傅拉，有排唔洗upgrade好過啦"},{"pid":"098c484567d61a5ccc356d3b97f5ec88569d0ff3","tid":261423,"uid":19463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>too long didn't read<br />\n同裝修師傳講邊度要上網 邊度做個位比你<br />\n之後再搵上網公司穿線</blockquote><br />\n搵上網公司隨時拉d四芯俾你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且都唔一定幫你拉<br />\n自己買一箱100M嘅 cat6俾師傅拉，有排唔洗upgrade好過啦</blockquote><br />\nCat6a/7都得"},{"pid":"941539b828d49d81ab5b34e5116b595423a8e58b","tid":261423,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"建議拉得,一間房拉兩個port<br />\n<br />\n剩router ok, 睇您有幾多port<br />\n唔夠用switch 再分咁解"},{"pid":"bd6a327ddbfcbb49f12af0798e4eab7e57cbc231","tid":261423,"uid":536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"叫裝修佬做喉 一間房兩個位應該都夠 最好叫佢地拉獨立線 咁就make sure 到每個位置行得足1000m , 其實cat5e 都夠晒1000m , cat6 以上d 線粗d ,條喉未必夠放咁多線<br />\n利申前pxxw 員工"},{"pid":"279c2880460b75d28e314494200b54c0fae4d0d9","tid":261423,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>too long didn't read<br />\n同裝修師傳講邊度要上網 邊度做個位比你<br />\n之後再搵上網公司穿線</blockquote><br />\n搵上網公司隨時拉d四芯俾你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且都唔一定幫你拉<br />\n自己買一箱100M嘅 cat6俾師傅拉，有排唔洗upgrade好過啦</blockquote><br />\nCat6a/7都得</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bd732a40383873076d9004b13c218763418454","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"舊位如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s1f947wb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs1f947wb&h=3e62da79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新位如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ycp12ieq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fycp12ieq&h=60cb94e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24e44602a91efa0f7ee893ff9593686d232be45e","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"師傅話舊位條喉唔改，舊電話位變成過路箱，分別造2條20mm喉去新Lan位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5ur19myd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5ur19myd&h=e39e0d2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35b84b477645f92859f0e3f533313fff1f73f198","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"師傅話有2個穿線方法<br />\n<br />\n方法一<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6v9h71jp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6v9h71jp&h=54ad3b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法二<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wxmepdn4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwxmepdn4&h=d500737b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得方法二好d，因為用方法一嘅話，果個位置就要放Router，但係附近冇打算做13A插蘇，要拉拖版唔方便。"},{"pid":"8fbde0d486c1e0df104954a1f7ce6489a91642f7","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"我個TP-Link Router放電腦位果邊"},{"pid":"5574b1f1f571c8b8c6f986cc537409235ffc415c","tid":261423,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"街線入廳，留個低壓線管，光纖入廳，放modem router<br />\n<br />\n廳再獨立管射入房，行雙線兩port, 咁就可以上網加hdmi to LAN射埋mon出廳<br />\n<br />\n用果用n 卡裝pi 加moonlight可以經lan低pin remote打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a336a6974eaf290081520fc25422cc6a77410caf","tid":261423,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街線入廳，留個低壓線管，光纖入廳，放modem router<br />\n<br />\n廳再獨立管射入房，行雙線兩port, 咁就可以上網加hdmi to LAN射埋mon出廳<br />\n<br />\n用果用n 卡裝pi 加moonlight可以經lan低pin remote打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a